Hartford.rb
===========

This is the website for the Hartford Ruby Brigade.

Installation
===========
sudo gem install merb-core merb-more dm-core dm-more do_mysql rspec ruby-openid
git clone git://github.com/actsasflinn/hartford.rb.git
cd hartford.rb
cp config/database.yml.example config/database.yml
rake db:create
rake sessions:create
rake db:automigrate

To make a home page
merb
open http://0.0.0.0:4000/admin/pages/new
create a page with a slug = home